{"data":[{"name":"75:1","price":"ഉയിര്‍ത്തെഴുന്നേല്‍പിന്‍റെ നാളുകൊണ്ട് ഞാനിതാ സത്യം ചെയ്യുന്നു.","arabic":"لَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5552,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"lā uq'simu biyawmi al-qiyāmati ","translations":["Nay","I swear","by (the) Day","(of) the Resurrection","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","uq'simu","biyawmi","al-qiyāmati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2540],[2,2540,3370],[3,3370,4250],[4,4250,6015]]}},{"name":"75:2","price":"കുറ്റപ്പെടുത്തുന്ന മനസ്സിനെക്കൊണ്ടും ഞാന്‍ സത്യം ചെയ്തു പറയുന്നു.","arabic":"وَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلنَّفۡسِ ٱللَّوَّامَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5553,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"walā uq'simu bil-nafsi al-lawāmati ","translations":["And nay","I swear","by the soul","self-accusing","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","uq'simu","bil-nafsi","al-lawāmati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2440],[2,2440,3280],[3,3280,5300],[4,5300,7415]]}},{"name":"75:3","price":"മനുഷ്യന്‍ വിചാരിക്കുന്നുണ്ടോ; നാം അവന്‍റെ എല്ലുകളെ ഒരുമിച്ചുകൂട്ടുകയില്ലെന്ന്‌?(1)","arabic":"أَيَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ أَلَّن نَّجۡمَعَ عِظَامَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5554,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"1) 'ഞങ്ങള്‍ മണ്ണും അസ്ഥിശകലങ്ങളുമായി മാറിക്കഴിഞ്ഞാലും ഞങ്ങള്‍ ഉയര്‍ത്തെഴുന്നേല്പിക്കപ്പെടുമോ?' എന്നു ചോദിച്ചിരുന്നവരോടാണ് ഈ ചോദ്യം. ഒരിക്കല്‍ മനുഷ്യശരീരത്തെ ശരിയായ വ്യവസ്ഥയില്‍ സംവിധാനിച്ചവന് ചിന്നിച്ചിതറിയ അസ്ഥിശകലങ്ങളെ പുനഃസംയോജിപ്പിക്കുക ഒട്ടും വിഷമകരമാവില്ല.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"ayaḥsabu al-insānu allan najmaʿa ʿiẓāmahu ","translations":["Does think","[the] man","that not","We will assemble","his bones","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["ayaḥsabu","al-insānu","allan","najmaʿa","ʿiẓāmahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1070],[2,1070,3170],[3,3170,3850],[4,3850,5510],[5,5510,7155]]}},{"name":"75:4","price":"അതെ, നാം അവന്‍റെ വിരല്‍ത്തുമ്പുകളെ പോലും ശരിപ്പെടുത്താന്‍ കഴിവുള്ളവനായിരിക്കെ.(2)","arabic":"بَلَىٰ قَٰدِرِينَ عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّسَوِّيَ بَنَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5555,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"2) കോടാനുകോടി മനുഷ്യരില്‍ ഓരോരുത്തരുടെയും വിരല്‍ത്തുമ്പുകള്‍ തികച്ചും വ്യത്യസ്തമാണ്. തിരിച്ചറിയാനുള്ള ഒരിക്കലും മാറിപ്പോകാത്ത ഉപാധിയത്രെ വിരലടയാളം. വിരല്‍തുമ്പുകളുടെ വലുപ്പത്തിലുള്ള ആനുപാതിക വ്യത്യാസവും അത്യന്തം പ്രയോജനകരമാണ്. അതു കൊണ്ടാണ് എഴുത്തും മറ്റും എളുപ്പമാകുന്നത്. ഇതൊക്കെ അല്ലാഹുവിന്റെ സൃഷ്ടി വൈഭവത്തിന്റെ ഉത്തമ നിദര്‍ശനമത്രെ.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"balā qādirīna ʿalā an nusawwiya banānahu ","translations":["Nay","(We are) Able","on","that","We can restore","his fingertips","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["balā","qādirīna","ʿalā","an","nusawwiya","banānahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1960],[3,1960,3790],[4,3790,4080],[5,4080,5770],[6,5770,7395]]}},{"name":"75:5","price":"പക്ഷെ (എന്നിട്ടും) മനുഷ്യന്‍ അവന്‍റെ ഭാവി ജീവിതത്തില്‍ തോന്നിവാസം ചെയ്യാന്‍ ഉദ്ദേശിക്കുന്നു.","arabic":"بَلۡ يُرِيدُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ لِيَفۡجُرَ أَمَامَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5556,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"bal yurīdu al-insānu liyafjura amāmahu ","translations":["Nay","Desires","[the] man","to give (the) lie","(to) what is before him","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["bal","yurīdu","al-insānu","liyafjura","amāmahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,1230],[3,1230,3120],[4,3120,4170],[5,4170,5635]]}},{"name":"75:6","price":"എപ്പോഴാണ് ഈ ഉയിര്‍ത്തെഴുന്നേല്‍പിന്‍റെ നാള്‍ എന്നവന്‍ ചോദിക്കുന്നു.","arabic":"يَسۡـَٔلُ أَيَّانَ يَوۡمُ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5557,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"yasalu ayyāna yawmu al-qiyāmati ","translations":["He asks","When","(is the) Day","(of) the Resurrection","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["yasalu","ayyāna","yawmu","al-qiyāmati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,900],[2,900,1870],[3,1870,2540],[4,2540,4395]]}},{"name":"75:7","price":"എന്നാല്‍ കണ്ണഞ്ചിപ്പോയാൽ.","arabic":"فَإِذَا بَرِقَ ٱلۡبَصَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5558,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-idhā bariqa al-baṣaru ","translations":["So when","is dazzled","the vision","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-idhā","bariqa","al-baṣaru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,1480],[3,1480,2675]]}},{"name":"75:8","price":"ചന്ദ്രന്ന് ഗ്രഹണം ബാധിക്കുകയും","arabic":"وَخَسَفَ ٱلۡقَمَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5559,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wakhasafa al-qamaru ","translations":["And becomes dark","the moon","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wakhasafa","al-qamaru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,2005]]}},{"name":"75:9","price":"സൂര്യനും ചന്ദ്രനും ഒരുമിച്ചുകൂട്ടപ്പെടുകയും ചെയ്താല്‍!","arabic":"وَجُمِعَ ٱلشَّمۡسُ وَٱلۡقَمَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5560,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wajumiʿa al-shamsu wal-qamaru ","translations":["And are joined","the sun","and the moon","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wajumiʿa","al-shamsu","wal-qamaru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1740],[3,1740,3075]]}},{"name":"75:10","price":"അന്നേ ദിവസം മനുഷ്യന്‍ പറയും; എവിടെയാണ് ഓടിരക്ഷപ്പെടാനുള്ളതെന്ന്‌.","arabic":"يَقُولُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ يَوۡمَئِذٍ أَيۡنَ ٱلۡمَفَرُّ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5561,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"yaqūlu al-insānu yawma-idhin ayna al-mafaru ","translations":["Will say","[the] man","that Day","Where","(is) the escape","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["yaqūlu","al-insānu","yawma-idhin","ayna","al-mafaru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,820],[2,820,2870],[3,2870,4100],[